tgt_text: He came to what was his own, but his own people did not receive him.

su_text: Tapi loba oge anu narima jeung palercaya ka Anjeunna teh; jelema-jelema anu kitu ku Anjeunna dipaparin hak jadi putra-putra Allah.
tgt_text: But to all who have received him - those who believe in his name - he has given the right to become God's children

su_text: Jadina putra-putra Allah teh lain ku cara anu lumrah di manusa, lain ku cara anu yuga ti bapa sipat manusa; Rama maranehna teh Allah ku manten.
tgt_text: - children not born by human parents or by human desire or a husband's decision, but by God.

su_text: Hal Anjeunna, kieu ditetelakeunana ku Yohanes, "Anjeunna teh nya eta anu ceuk kami kieu tea, 'Sumping-Na pandeurieun kami, tapi ngungkulan kami, reh Anjeunna mah memeh kami dijurukeun oge geus jumeneng.'"
tgt_text: John testified about him and shouted out, "This one was the one about whom I said, 'He who comes after me is greater than I am, because he existed before me.'"

su_text: Jelema can aya anu geus ningal Allah.
tgt_text: No one has ever seen God.

su_text: Para gegeden urang Yahudi di Yerusalem ngutus sawatara imam jeung jelema-jelema urang Lewi, nanyakeun kieu ka Yohanes, "Anjeun teh saha?"
tgt_text: Now this was John's testimony when the Jewish leaders sent priests and Levites from Jerusalem to ask him, "Who are you?"

su_text: "Upami sanes, saha?" ceuk utusan, "Anjeun teh Elias?" "Lain, lain eta," waler Yohanes.
tgt_text: Are you Elijah?" He said, "I am not!" "Are you the Prophet?" He answered, "No!"

su_text: Cobi, ceuk anjeun, anjeun teh saha?"
tgt_text: What do you say about yourself?"

su_text: Yohanes ngawalerna ku pilahir Nabi Yesaya: "Kaula teh, 'Soara anu cumeluk di gurun keusik: Sadiakeun jalan anu lempeng, pikeun Pangeran!'"
tgt_text: John said, "I amthe voice of one shouting in the wilderness, 'Make straightthe way for the Lord,'as Isaiah the prophet said."

su_text: naranya deui, "Kristus sanes, Elias sanes, Nabi tea sanes, naha atuh anjeun ngabaptis?"
tgt_text: So they asked John, "Why then are you baptizing if you are not the Christ, nor Elijah, nor the Prophet?"

su_text: Waler Yohanes, "Kaula ngabaptis teh ku cai.
tgt_text: John answered them, "I baptize with water.

su_text: Eta kajadian teh di Betania sisi Walungan Yordan peuntas wetan, paragi Yohanes ngabaptis.
tgt_text: These things happened in Bethany across the Jordan River where John was baptizing.

su_text: Poe isukna Yohanes ningali Yesus anu rek ka anjeunna.
tgt_text: On the next day John saw Jesus coming toward him and said, "Look, the Lamb of God who takes away the sin of the world!

su_text: Tapi kami ngabaptis ku cai teh nya eta pikeun ngenalkeun Anjeunna ka bangsa Israil."
tgt_text: I did not recognize him, but I came baptizing with water so that he could be revealed to Israel."

su_text: Geus kitu Yohanes ngucapkeun panyaksi kieu, "Kami geus nenjo Anjeunna diauban ku Roh Allah anu lungsur ti sawarga ngarupakeun manuk japati.
tgt_text: Then John testified, "I saw the Spirit descending like a dove from heaven, and it remained on him.

su_text: Tapi memeh eta kami geus didawuhan kieu ku Allah, anu ngutus kami supaya ngabaptis ku cai, 'Maneh bakal nenjo Roh Kami ti sawarga turun ka hiji jelema; nya Anjeunna engke anu bakal ngabaptis ku Roh Suci.'
tgt_text: And I did not recognize him, but the one who sent me to baptize with water said to me, 'The one on whom you see the Spirit descending and remaining - this is the one who baptizes with the Holy Spirit.'

su_text: Poe isukna deui, waktu Yohanes keur ngadeg di tempat kamari jeung dua muridna,
tgt_text: Again the next day John was standing there with two of his disciples.

su_text: Sanggeus anjeunna ngalahir kitu, eta dua murid teh arindit naluturkeun ka Yesus.
tgt_text: When John's two disciples heard him say this, they followed Jesus.

su_text: Yesus nyoreang, ningalieun ka nu naluturkeun tuluy mariksa, "Keur nareangan naon?" Jawabna, "Di mana Rabi linggih?" (Rabi hartina "Guru").
tgt_text: Jesus turned around and saw them following and said to them, "What do you want?" So they said to him, "Rabbi" (which is translated Teacher), "where are you staying?"

su_text: Gancang Andreas manggihan Simon, tuluy nyarita, "Kuring geus papanggih jeung Mesias." (Mesias teh hartina "Kristus", Jurusalamet.)
tgt_text: He first found his own brother Simon and told him, "We have found the Messiah!" (which is translated Christ).

su_text: Yesus neuteup ka Simon, tuluy ngalahir, "Ngaran maneh Simon, anak Yonas.
tgt_text: Jesus looked at him and said, "You are Simon, the son of John.

su_text: Tapi maneh bakal disebut Kepas." (Kepas saharti keneh jeung Petrus, nya eta "batu karang".)
tgt_text: You will be called Cephas" (which is translated Peter).

su_text: Simon tuluy dideuheuskeun ka Yesus.
tgt_text: Andrew brought Simon to Jesus.

su_text: Poe isukna Yesus angkat ka Galilea.
tgt_text: On the next day Jesus wanted to set out for Galilee.

su_text: Anjeunna pendak jeung Pilipus, tuluy diajak, saur-Na, "Milu ka Kami!"
tgt_text: He found Philip and said to him, "Follow me."

su_text: (Pilipus asal ti Betsaida, lemburna Andreas jeung Petrus.)
tgt_text: (Now Philip was from Bethsaida, the town of Andrew and Peter.)

su_text: Pilipus manggihan Natanael, nyarita, "Kuring geus papanggih jeung anu disebut-sebut ku Musa dina Kitab Hukum Allah jeung anu ditulis ku nabi-nabi tea.
tgt_text: Philip found Nathanael and told him, "We have found the one Moses wrote about in the law, and the prophets also wrote about - Jesus of Nazareth, the son of Joseph."

su_text: "Na aya kitu anu hade ti Nasaret?" Natanael nanya.
tgt_text: Nathanael replied, "Can anything good come out of Nazareth?" Philip replied, "Come and see."

su_text: Barang ningali Natanael datang, Yesus terus ngalahir ngeunaan dirina, saur-Na, "Tah ieu urang Israil tulen, taya pisan kapalsuanana!"
tgt_text: Jesus saw Nathanael coming toward him and exclaimed, "Look, a true Israelitein whom there is no deceit!"

su_text: "Geuning Bapa uninga ka abdi?" Natanael nanya.
tgt_text: Nathanael asked him, "How do you know me?" Jesus replied, "Before Philip called you, when you were under the fig tree, I saw you."

su_text: "Pa Guru!" jawab Natanael, "Pa Guru teh geuning Putra Allah!
tgt_text: Nathanael answered him, "Rabbi, you are the Son of God; you are the king of Israel!"

su_text: Saur Yesus, "Maneh percaya kitu teh naha pedah bieu Kami nyebutkeun yen maneh ku Kami katenjo handapeun tangkal kondang?
tgt_text: Jesus said to him, "Because I told you that I saw you under the fig tree, do you believe?

su_text: Loba keneh anu leuwih aheng, bakal kasaksian ku maneh."
tgt_text: You will see greater things than these."

su_text: Saur-Na deui ka sarerea, "Sing percaya kana benerna ieu omongan Kami: Maraneh bakal narenjo langit muka, para malaikat turun unggah ti sawarga ka Putra Manusa." Yohanes 2
tgt_text: He continued, "I tell all of you the solemn truth - you will see heaven opened and the angels of God ascending and descending on the Son of Man." Yohanes 2

su_text: Bapa budak teh ingeteun, jam eta pisan kamari Yesus ngadawuh-Na, "Anak maneh tangtu hirup." Manehna jeung sakulawargana jadi palercaya ka Yesus.
tgt_text: Then the father realized that it was the very time Jesus had said to him, "Your son will live," and he himself believed along with his entire household.

su_text: Yohanes 5
tgt_text: Yohanes 5

su_text: Eta kaajaiban teh anu kadua anu dipidamel ku Yesus di Galilea, sanggeus sumping ti Yudea.
tgt_text: Jesus did this as his second miraculous sign when he returned from Judea to Galilee.

su_text: Sabab daging Kami teh sajatina kadaharan, getih Kami sajatina inuman.
tgt_text: For my flesh is true food, and my blood is true drink.

su_text: Anu ngadahar daging Kami jeung nginum getih Kami, bakal hirup di Kami, nya kitu deui Kami bakal hirup di manehna.
tgt_text: The one who eats my flesh and drinks my blood resides in me, and I in him.

su_text: Kami diutus ku Rama anu jumeneng hirup, sarta ku karana Mantenna Kami oge hirup.
tgt_text: Just as the living Father sent me, and I live because of the Father, so the one who consumes me will live because of me.

su_text: Anu ngadahar ieu roti bakal hirup salalanggengna.
tgt_text: The one who eats this bread will live forever."

su_text: Yesus ngawulangkeun hal ieu teh di Kapernaum, di imah ibadah.
tgt_text: Jesus said these things while he was teaching in the synagogue in Capernaum.

su_text: Saha nu bisa narima?"
tgt_text: Who can understand it?"

su_text: Loba panganut Yesus anu ngaromongkeun eta piwulang, pokna, "Beurat teuing eta pangajaran teh!
tgt_text: Then many of his disciples, when they heard these things, said, "This is a difficult saying!

su_text: Yesus oge uningaeun yen loba anu ngaromel kitu, tuluy ngalahir ka maranehna, "Maraneh rek malundur ku hal ieu?
tgt_text: When Jesus was aware that his disciples were complaining about this, he said to them, "Does this cause you to be offended?

su_text: Anu mere hirup teh Roh Allah, kakuatan manusa mah taya gunana naon-naon.
tgt_text: The Spirit is the one who gives life; human nature is of no help!

su_text: Tapi di maraneh aya anu henteu palercaya kana hal eta." (Ti samemehna oge Yesus memang geus uningaeun, mana nu bakal moal percaya, jeung saha anu bakal ngahianat ka Anjeunna.)
tgt_text: But there are some of you who do not believe." (For Jesus had already known from the beginning who those were who did not believe, and who it was who would betray him.)

su_text: Pilahir-Na deui, "Nya ieu sababna nu matak Kami nyebutkeun yen moal aya anu bisa datang ka Kami lamun lain ku pangersa Rama."
tgt_text: So Jesus added, "Because of this I told you that no one can come to me unless the Father has allowed him to come."

su_text: "Gusti," ceuk Simon Petrus, "ka saha abdi-abdi kedah indit upami ngantunkeun?
tgt_text: Simon Peter answered him, "Lord, to whom would we go?

su_text: Gusti nu kagungan pangandika nu maparin hirup langgeng.
tgt_text: You have the words of eternal life.

su_text: Abdi-abdi percanten, sareng yakin Gusti teh Utusan Suci ti Allah."
tgt_text: We have come to believe and to know that you are the Holy One of God!"

su_text: Pilahir Yesus, "Kami milih maraneh teh dua welas urang, lain?
tgt_text: Jesus replied, "Didn't I choose you, the twelve, and yet one of you is the devil?"

su_text: Anu dimaksad ku Anjeunna nya eta Yudas bin Simon Iskariot, sabab manehna enya oge murid Anjeunna keneh, engkena bakal ngahianat ka Anjeunna.
tgt_text: (Now he said this about Judas son of Simon Iscariot, for Judas, one of the twelve, was going to betray him.) Yohanes 7

su_text: Sanggeus Musa, abdi Allah tea pupus, PANGERAN nimbalan ka pangbantuna Musa, nya eta Yosua putra Nun.
tgt_text: After Moses theLord's servant died, theLordsaid to Joshua son of Nun, Moses' assistant:

su_text: Timbalana-Na, "Musa abdi Kami geus tilar dunya.
tgt_text: "Moses my servant is dead.

su_text: Ku sabab eta sing teteg, sing yakin; jeung masing satia ka sakabeh Hukum anu dibikeun ka maneh ku Musa, abdi Kami tea.
tgt_text: Carefully obey all the law my servant Moses charged you to keep!

su_text: Upama kitu hirup maneh tan wande senang sarta hasil.
tgt_text: Then you will prosper and be successful.

su_text: Ulah sieun atawa leutik hate, sabab Kami, PANGERAN Allah maneh ka mana-mana oge tan wande nyarengan."
tgt_text: Don't be afraid and don't panic, for I, theLordyour God, am with you in all you do."

su_text: Ti dinya Yosua miwarangan para pamingpin sina ka pakemahan, sangkan marentahkeun jalma-jalma,
tgt_text: Joshua instructed the leaders of the people:

su_text: "Geura saradia dahareun keur bekel, sabab tilu poe deui maraneh kudu meuntasan Walungan Yordan, baris maratuh di tanah anu rek dipaparinkeun ku PANGERAN Allah maraneh."
tgt_text: "Go through the camp and command the people, 'Prepare your supplies, for within three days you will cross the Jordan River and begin the conquest of the land theLordyour God is ready to hand over to you.'"

su_text: Yosua sasauran ka kaom Rubin, kaom Gad jeung ka satengahna kaom Menase,
tgt_text: Joshua told the Reubenites, Gadites, and the half tribe of Manasseh:

su_text: Jawab maranehna ka Yosua, "Sadaya pisaur anjeun tan wande dijalankeun.
tgt_text: They told Joshua, "We will do everything you say.

su_text: Mugia PANGERAN Allah nyarengan ka anjeun sakumaha ka Musa!
tgt_text: But may theLordyour God be with you as he was with Moses!

su_text: Sing saha anu ngalawan kana kakawasaan anjeun atanapi wangkelang kana parentah, baris dipaehan.
tgt_text: Any man who rebels against what you say and does not obey all your commands will be executed.

su_text: Sing percanten, teu kedah salempang!" Yosua 2
tgt_text: But be strong and brave!" Yosua 2

su_text: Pohara sarieuneunana urang ditu ku urang teh." Yosua 3
tgt_text: All who live in the land are cringing before us!" Yosua 3

su_text: Tapi Rahab dayang tea jeung kabeh kulawargana ku Yosua dirahayukeun, dumeh geus nulungan nyumputkeun dua mata-mata anu lolongok ka Yeriho tea.
tgt_text: Yet Joshua spared Rahab the prostitute, her father's family, and all who belonged to her.

su_text: Harita Yosua ngedalkeun hiji supata, saurna, "Sing saha anu nyoba-nyoba ngadegkeun deui ieu kota Yeriho, tangtu disapa ku PANGERAN.
tgt_text: At that time Joshua made this solemn declaration: "The man who attempts to rebuild this city of Jericho will stand condemned before theLord.

su_text: Anu nyieun pademenna mangka paeh anak cikalna; Anu ngadegkeun lawangna mangka paeh anak bungsuna."
tgt_text: He will lose his firstborn son when he lays its foundations and his youngest son when he erects its gates!"

su_text: Yosua 7
tgt_text: Yosua 7

su_text: Yosua jadi kamashur ka sakuliah tanah eta.
tgt_text: TheLordwas with Joshua and he became famous throughout the land.

su_text: Ari raja Ai ku anjeunna digantung dina patok, mayitna diantep nepi ka burit.
tgt_text: He hung the king of Ai on a tree, leaving him exposed until evening.

su_text: Geus kitu Yosua ngadegkeun altar di Gunung Ebal kanggo PANGERAN, Allahna Israil.
tgt_text: Then Joshua built an altar for theLordGod of Israel on Mount Ebal,

su_text: Kasaksian ku urang Israil, dina eta batu Yosua ngadamel salinan Hukum anu diserat ku Musa tea.
tgt_text: There, in the presence of the Israelites, Joshua inscribed on the stones a duplicate of the law written by Moses.

su_text: Urang Israil jeung para pangurusna, kapala-kapala baladna, hakim-hakimna, kitu deui jalma piluaran nu araya di maranehna, nararangtung kenca katuhueun Peti Perjangjian PANGERAN, nyalanghareup ka imam-imam kaom Lewi anu ngagotong eta peti.
tgt_text: All the people, rulers, leaders, and judges were standing on either side of the ark, in front of the Levitical priests who carried the ark of the covenant of theLord.

su_text: Ti dinya saeusining Hukum teh ku Yosua diaos bedas, kitu deui hal piberkaheunana jeung panyapana, sakumaha anu kaungel dina kitab Hukum.
tgt_text: Then Joshua read aloud all the words of the law, including the blessings and the curses, just as they are written in the law scroll.

su_text: Yosua 9
tgt_text: Yosua 9

su_text: Tiap-tiap Hukum Musa teh ku Yosua diaoskeun ka sakabeh nu karumpul, kaasup awewe jeung barudak, kitu deui urang piluaran anu araya di maranehna.
tgt_text: Joshua read aloud every commandment Moses had given before the whole assembly of Israel, including the women, children, and resident foreigners who lived among them.

su_text: Sabada eta, Yosua sabaladna ti Eglon naranjak ka pasir muru ka Hebron.
tgt_text: Joshua and all Israel marched up from Eglon to Hebron and fought against it.

su_text: Debir katut rajana ku Yosua dijieun cara ka nagri Hebron jeung Libna jeung ka raja-rajana.
tgt_text: They did to Debir and its king what they had done to Libnah and its king and to Hebron.

su_text: Panarajang Yosua ti Kades Barnea diteruskeun ka kidul, ka Gasa di deukeut basisir, kitu deui sakuliah tanah Gosen nepi ka tanah Gibon di kaler.
tgt_text: Joshua conquered the area between Kadesh Barnea and Gaza and the whole region of Goshen, all the way to Gibeon.

su_text: Raja-rajana katut wilayah-wilayahna sakali ngagempur beunang kabeh ku Yosua, sabab urang Israil dipangmerangankeun ku PANGERAN Allahna.
tgt_text: Joshua captured in one campaign all these kings and their lands, for theLordGod of Israel fought for Israel.

su_text: Yosua 11
tgt_text: Yosua 11

su_text: Sabada eta, Yosua sabaladna marulang deui ka pakemahan di Gilgal.
tgt_text: Then Joshua and all Israel returned to the camp at Gilgal.

su_text: Kehila, Aksib jeung Maresa; jumlahna salapan kota katut desa-desa sakurilingeunana.
tgt_text: Keilah, Aczib, and Mareshah - a total of nine cities and their towns.

su_text: Ekron katut desa-desa jeung lembur-lemburna,
tgt_text: Ekron and its surrounding towns and settlements;

su_text: jeung sakabeh kota katut desa-desana deukeut Asdod, ti Ekron nepi ka basisir Laut Tengah.
tgt_text: from Ekron westward, all those in the vicinity of Ashdod and their towns;

su_text: Asdod jeung Gasa, katut desa-desa jeung lembur-lemburna, kebat tepi ka anak walungan wates Mesir jeung basisir Laut Tengah.
tgt_text: Ashdod with its surrounding towns and settlements, and Gaza with its surrounding towns and settlements, as far as the Stream of Egypt and the border at the Mediterranean Sea.

su_text: Kota-kota pagununganana: Samir, Yatir, Soko,
tgt_text: These cities were in the hill country: Shamir, Jattir, Socoh,

su_text: Anab, Estemoa, Anim,
tgt_text: Anab, Eshtemoh, Anim,

su_text: Gosen, Holon jeung Gilo; jumlahna sawelas kota katut desa-desa sakurilingeunana.
tgt_text: Goshen, Holon, and Giloh - a total of eleven cities and their towns.

su_text: Oge: Arab, Duma, Esan,
tgt_text: Arab, Dumah, Eshan,

su_text: Yanim, Bet Tapua, Apeka,
tgt_text: Janim, Beth Tappuah, Aphekah,

su_text: Humta, Hebron jeung Sior; salapan kota katut desa-desa sakurilingeunana.
tgt_text: Humtah, Kiriath Arba (that is, Hebron), and Zior - a total of nine cities and their towns.

su_text: Oge: Maon, Karmel, Sip, Yuta,
tgt_text: Maon, Carmel, Ziph, Juttah,

su_text: Yisrel, Yokdam, Sanoah,
tgt_text: Jezreel, Jokdeam, Zanoah,

su_text: Kain, Gibea jeung Timna; sapuluh kota katut desa-desa sakurilingeunana.
tgt_text: Kain, Gibeah, and Timnah - a total of ten cities and their towns.

su_text: Oge: Halhul, Bet Sur, Gedor,
tgt_text: Halhul, Beth Zur, Gedor,

su_text: Maarat, Bet Anot jeung Eltekon; genep kota katut desa-desa sakurilingeunana.
tgt_text: Maarath, Beth Anoth, and Eltekon - a total of six cities and their towns.

su_text: Oge: Kiryat Baal (atawa Kiryat Yarim) jeung Raba; dua kota katut desa-desa sakurilingeunana.
tgt_text: Kiriath Baal (that is, Kiriath Jearim) and Rabbah - a total of two cities and their towns.

su_text: Kota-kota anu di gurun keusik nya eta: Bet Araba, Midin, Sekaka,
tgt_text: These cities were in the desert: Beth Arabah, Middin, Secacah,

su_text: Nibsan, Kota Uyah jeung En Gedi; genep kota katut desa-desa sakurilingeunana.
tgt_text: Nibshan, the city of Salt, and En Gedi - a total of six cities and their towns.

su_text: Yosua 16
tgt_text: Yosua 16

su_text: Tapi urang Yebus mah anu maratuh di Yerusalem ku urang Yuda henteu bisa disingkahkeun.
tgt_text: The men of Judah were unable to conquer the Jebusites living in Jerusalem.

su_text: Nepi ka ayeuna oge urang Yebus mah araraya bae reujeung urang Yuda.
tgt_text: The Jebusites live with the people of Judah in Jerusalem to this very day.

su_text: Kahatur dumateng dulur-dulur, anu parantos disaur ku Allah, anu diauban ku kaasih Allah nu jumeneng Rama, anu diraksa ku Yesus Kristus.
tgt_text: From Jude, a slave of Jesus Christ and brother of James, to those who are called, wrapped in the love of God the Father and kept for Jesus Christ.

su_text: Sarta sing aringet oge, malaikat-malaikat anu parundung ti tempatna lantaran teu sarugema ku pangkatna, ku Allah diberok di tempat anu poek mongkleng di handap, dibarogod ku rante langgeng, ngadago hukumanana engke dina poe nu hebat.
tgt_text: You also know that the angels who did not keep within their proper domain but abandoned their own place of residence, he has kept in eternal chains in utter darkness, locked up for the judgment of the great Day.

su_text: Waktu anjeunna padu jeung Iblis parebut hak kana layon Musa, teu wantuneun nganggo kecap-kecap anu sipatna ngahina, ukur nyaurkeun kieu, "Sing dibendon anjeun ku Allah!"
tgt_text: But even when Michael the archangel was arguing with the devil and debating with him concerning Moses' body, he did not dare to bring a slanderous judgment, but said, "May the Lord rebuke you!"

su_text: Ari jelema-jelema anu kasebut bieu, geus wani ngayehkeun kana hal-hal anu tacan katepi ku pangartina, kakara ceuk nalurina anu henteu jeung pikiran, kawas sato bae.
tgt_text: But these men do not understand the things they slander, and they are being destroyed by the very things that, like irrational animals, they instinctively comprehend.

su_text: Pasti cilaka eta jelema-jelema teh!
tgt_text: Woe to them!

su_text: Kalakuanana ibarat mega ditiup angin tapi teu nurunkeun hujan; ibarat tangkal nu tara buahan kajeun keur usum, cara tangkal anu geus rungkad jeung akar-akarna, kawas tangkal paeh.
tgt_text: They are waterless clouds, carried along by the winds; autumn trees without fruit - twice dead, uprooted;

su_text: kersa-Na mariksa perkara sakabeh jelema, baris ngahukum ka sakur anu kalakuanana doraka, anu omong-omonganana nyarogok ngalawan ka Mantenna!"
tgt_text: to execute judgment on all, and to convict every person of all their thoroughly ungodly deeds that they have committed, and of all the harsh words that ungodly sinners have spoken against him."

su_text: Tapi dulur-dulur sing aringet kana kasauran rasul-rasulna Gusti urang Yesus Kristus, bareto.
tgt_text: But you, dear friends - recall the predictions foretold by the apostles of our Lord Jesus Christ.

su_text: Geuning saur aranjeunna kieu, "Mun geus deukeut kana ahir jaman, bakal aya anu daratang maroyokan ka aranjeun, jalma-jalma purah ngumbar napsu anu doraka."
tgt_text: For they said to you, "In the end time there will come scoffers, propelled by their own ungodly desires."

su_text: Sing hirup nyalindung kana asihing Allah, sapanjang aranjeun ngaharepkeun nugraha Gusti urang Yesus Kristus, anu baris nyandak urang kana hirup anu sayakti jeung langgeng.
tgt_text: maintain yourselves in the love of God, while anticipating the mercy of our Lord Jesus Christ that brings eternal life.

su_text: Ka Mantenna, anu kawasa ngaraksa ka aranjeun sangkan hirup aranjeun henteu labuh, anu kawasa nyandak aranjeun ka payuneun kamulyaana-Na dina kaayaan bagja jeung tanpa cela,
tgt_text: Now to the one who is able to keep you from falling, and to cause you to stand, rejoicing, without blemish before his glorious presence,

su_text: Amin.
tgt_text: Amen.

su_text: ka Mantenna, Allah nu jadi Jurusalamet urang ku karana Yesus Kristus Gusti urang, kasanggakeun kamulyaan, kaagungan, kadigjayaan jeung kakawasaan, ti baheula-baheula, nepi ka ayeuna, nepi ka engke, salalanggengna!
tgt_text: to the only God our Savior through Jesus Christ our Lord, be glory, majesty, power, and authority, before all time, and now, and for all eternity.

su_text: Tapi PANGERAN ngadatangkeun angin ribut di laut, topan kacida gedena nepi ka kapal meh bejad.
tgt_text: But theLordhurled a powerful wind on the sea.

su_text: Matros-matros ngaromong pada batur, "Urang lotrekeun, supaya kanyahoan saha nu jadi gara-gara nepi ka urang nyorang ieu bahla." Sanggeus dilotre, lotrena keuna ka jenengan Yunus.
tgt_text: The sailors said to one another, "Come on, let's cast lots to find out whose fault it is that this disaster has overtaken us." So they cast lots, and Jonah was singled out.

su_text: Anjeun asal ti mana?
tgt_text: Where do you come from?

su_text: Bangsa naon?"
tgt_text: What's your country?

su_text: Kaula ngabakti ka PANGERAN, Allah nu jumeneng di sawarga, nu ngadamel daratan jeung lautan." Saterusna anjeunna nerangkeun yen keur minggat ti PANGERAN.
tgt_text: And I worship theLord, the God of heaven, who made the sea and the dry land."

su_text: Ku sabab kitu maranehna sasambat ka PANGERAN, "Duh PANGERAN, mugi abdi-abdi sadaya ulah dihukum dugi ka tiwas, wireh abdi-abdi kapaksa kedah ngorbankeun ieu jalmi!
tgt_text: So they cried out to theLord, "Oh, please,Lord, don't let us die on account of this man!

su_text: Geus kitu Yunus ku maranehna digotong, tuluy dialungkeun ka laut.
tgt_text: So they picked Jonah up and threw him into the sea, and the sea stopped raging.

su_text: Matros-matros jadi kacida sarieuneunana ku PANGERAN, nepi ka ngurban sarta jangji seja ngabakti ka Mantenna.
tgt_text: The men feared theLordgreatly, and earnestly vowed to offer lavish sacrifices to the Lord.

su_text: Yunus 2
tgt_text: Yunus 2

su_text: Dina bulan kadalapan taun kadua pamarentahan Darius raja Persia, PANGERAN maparin ieu amanat ka Nabi Jakaria bin Berekya putu Ido.
tgt_text: In the eighth month of Darius' second year, the word of theLordcame to the prophet Zechariah, son of Berechiah son of Iddo, as follows:

su_text: Geus kitu kakara tarobat jeung rarumasa yen Kami, PANGERAN Nu Maha Kawasa, geus sapantesna ngahukum ka maranehna, satimpal jeung kalakuanana, sarta luyu jeung putusan Kami."
tgt_text: Then they paid attention and confessed, 'TheLordwho rules over all has indeed done what he said he would do to us, because of our sinful ways.'"

su_text: Dina taun kadua pamarentahan Raja Darius, dina tanggal dua puluh opat bulan kasabelas (Bulan Sebat), PANGERAN maparin ieu amanat suci ka sim kuring dina hiji titingalian ti peuting.
tgt_text: On the twenty-fourth day of the eleventh month, the month Shebat, in Darius' second year, the word of the Lord came to the prophet Zechariah son of Berechiah son of Iddo, as follows:

su_text: Di pungkureunana aya deui kuda sababaraha hiji, buluna aya nu beureum, nu belang, nu bodas.
tgt_text: Behind him were red, sorrel, and white horses.

su_text: Eta malaikat misaur, "Nun PANGERAN Nu Maha Kawasa, parantos tujuh puluh taun Gusti bendu ka Yerusalem sareng ka kota-kota di nagri Yuda.
tgt_text: The angel of theLordthen asked, "Lordwho rules over all, how long before you have compassion on Jerusalem and the other cities of Judah which you have been so angry with for these seventy years?"

su_text: Tapi Kami pohara jengkelna ka bangsa-bangsa anu keur garenah-genah ngararasakeun aman.
tgt_text: But I am greatly displeased with the nations that take my grace for granted.

su_text: Eta malaikat miwarang deui supaya kaula ngembarkeun kieu, "Dawuhan PANGERAN Nu Maha Kawasa, kota-kota Mantenna baris makmur deui, sarta Yerusalem bakal ditulungan sakali deui jeung bakal diangken yen jadi kota kagungana-Na."
tgt_text: Speak up again with the message of theLordwho rules over all: 'My cities will once more overflow with prosperity, and once more theLordwill comfort Zion and validate his choice of Jerusalem.'"

su_text: Sim kuring nanyakeun ka malaikat anu geus sasauran ka kaula tea, "Naon hartosna eta tanduk?" Waleranana, "Eta teh kakawasaan di dunya, anu ngawurkeun urang Yuda, urang Israil, jeung urang Yerusalem nepi ka pabalencar."
tgt_text: So I asked the angelic messenger who spoke with me, "What are these?" He replied, "These are the horns that have scattered Judah, Israel, and Jerusalem."

su_text: Kaula nanyakeun, "Eta bade naon?" Mantenna ngawaler, "Arek ngoyagkeun jeung ngagulingkeun bangsa-bangsa, anu geus ngaburak-barik Yuda jeung ngaburencaykeun jalma-jalmana." Zakharia 2
tgt_text: I asked, "What are these going to do?" He answered, "These horns are the ones that have scattered Judah so that there is no one to be seen.

su_text: Loba jalma jeung bangsa-bangsa anu kuat bakal daratang ka Yerusalem, seja ngabarakti ka PANGERAN Nu Maha Kawasa jeung menta berkah Mantenna.
tgt_text: Many peoples and powerful nations will come to Jerusalem to seek theLordwho rules over all and to ask his favor.

su_text: Harita, sapuluh jalma urang asing bakal datang ka urang Yahudi saurang ngaromong kieu, 'Kaula ge hayang bagja cara anjeun; rehna kaula nguping yen anjeun diberkahan ku Allah.'" Zakharia 9
tgt_text: TheLordwho rules over all says, 'In those days ten people from all languages and nations will grasp hold of - indeed, grab - the robe of one Jew and say, "Let us go with you, for we have heard that God is with you."'" Zakharia 9

su_text: Ieu pesen Allah ka Nabi Sepanya, putra Raja Hiskia anak Amarya anak Gedalya anak Kusi.
tgt_text: This is the prophetic message that the Lord gave to Zephaniah son of Cushi, son of Gedaliah, son of Amariah, son of Hezekiah.

su_text: Dipaparinkeunana keur jaman Yosia anak Amon jadi raja Yuda.
tgt_text: Zephaniah delivered this message during the reign of King Josiah son of Amon of Judah:

su_text: PANGERAN ngandika, "Sakeudeung deui Kami rek ngabasmi sagala rupa nu aya di bumi,
tgt_text: "I will destroy everything from the face of the earth," says theLord.

su_text: Rek ngabasmi sesa adat ibadah ka Baal anu aya keneh di dinya, sangkan ulah aya deui anu inget ka imam-imam brahala anu ngaladenan Baal.
tgt_text: I will remove from this place every trace of Baal worship, as well as the very memory of the pagan priests.

su_text: Kami rek ngahukum urang Yerusalem jeung urang Yuda.
tgt_text: "I will attack Judah and all who live in Jerusalem.

su_text: Timbalan PANGERAN, "Dina poean meuncitan, Kami rek ngahukum para gegeden, anak-anak raja, jeung sakabeh anu make adat bangsa lian.
tgt_text: "On the day of the Lord's sacrificial meal, I will punish the princes and the king's sons, and all who wear foreign styles of clothing.

su_text: Harta bandana bakal dirampas, imah-imahna bakal diburak-barik.
tgt_text: Their wealth will be stolen and their houses ruined!

su_text: Poe agung PANGERAN geus deukeut, deukeut naker, bakal gancang datang.
tgt_text: The Lord's great day of judgment is almost here; it is approaching very rapidly!

su_text: Eta poe pinuh ku hawa amarah, poe sangsara, poe tunggara, poe ngalebur, poe ngaruksak, poe poek, poe cilaka, poe mendung, poe kasaput ku mega,
tgt_text: That day will be a day of God's anger, a day of distress and hardship, a day of devastation and ruin, a day of darkness and gloom, a day of clouds and dark skies,

su_text: Sakuliah jagat baris kahuru ku seuneu wera-Na.
tgt_text: The whole earth will be consumed by his fiery wrath.
